{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Labs Disc Generator"], "type": "title", "extent": [0, 24], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [139, 192], "text": [" Create a polygon disc with uv\u2019s and normals "]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [192, 593], "text": ["The disc generator wraps up some common functionality for generating discs for realtime vfx (think AOE\u2019s or muzzle flashes). You can quickly set the inner and outer radius, modify the profile and add noise to shape the disc for multiple usecases. UV\u2019s are automatically laid out and adjusted with override controls. Add vertex colour based on u or v to drive material parameters in your game engine."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [642, 711], "text": ["Distance from the centre of the object for the inner circle."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Inner Radius"], "role": "item", "extent": [624, 642], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [729, 798], "text": ["Distance from the centre of the object for the outer circle."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Outer Radius"], "role": "item", "extent": [711, 729], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [813, 880], "text": ["Start point of the arc in degrees, relative to the x-axis."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Arc Start"], "role": "item", "extent": [798, 813], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [893, 958], "text": ["End point of the arc in degrees, relative to the x-axis."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Arc End"], "role": "item", "extent": [880, 893], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [974, 1026], "text": ["Number of polygon segments around the disc."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["U Segments"], "role": "item", "extent": [958, 974], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1042, 1124], "text": ["Number of polygon segments from the centre to the outer edge of the disc."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["V Segments"], "role": "item", "extent": [1026, 1042], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1143, 1209], "text": ["This essentially flips the u and v direction of the uv\u2019s."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Rotate UVs 90"], "role": "item", "extent": [1124, 1143], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1231, 1375], "text": ["The first two components set the coverage of the uv\u2019s in the u direction. The third component distorts the uv\u2019s using a power function."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["U Range And Bias"], "role": "item", "extent": [1209, 1231], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1397, 1541], "text": ["The first two components set the coverage of the uv\u2019s in the v direction. The third component distorts the uv\u2019s using a power function."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["V Range And Bias"], "role": "item", "extent": [1375, 1397], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1559, 1612], "text": ["Height of the inner circle along the y axis."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Inner Height"], "role": "item", "extent": [1541, 1559], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1630, 1683], "text": ["Height of the outer circle along the y axis."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Outer Height"], "role": "item", "extent": [1612, 1630], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1701, 1936], "text": ["When computing vertex normals, if normals of vertices around a single point are less than or equal to this angle (in degrees) apart from each other, they will be averaged together, weighted by the vertex angle in each polygon."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["N Cusp Angle"], "role": "item", "extent": [1683, 1701], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1957, 2018], "text": ["Increase or decrease the effect of the profile ramp."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Ramp Multiplier"], "role": "item", "extent": [1936, 1957], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2034, 2088], "text": ["Use the ramp to modify the shape of the disc."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Curve Ramp"], "role": "item", "extent": [2018, 2034], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Settings"], "extent": [605, 624], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2119, 2175], "text": ["Enable perlin noise distortion of the geometry."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Add Noise"], "role": "item", "extent": [2104, 2119], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2196, 2225], "text": ["Displacement amount."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Noise Intensity"], "role": "item", "extent": [2175, 2196], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2242, 2294], "text": ["Scale the noise independantly in each axis."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Noise Scale"], "role": "item", "extent": [2225, 2242], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2313, 2360], "text": ["The number of composited noise layers."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Noise Octaves"], "role": "item", "extent": [2294, 2313], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2378, 2415], "text": ["Distort the uv\u2019s with noise."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Add UV Noise"], "role": "item", "extent": [2360, 2378], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2433, 2482], "text": ["Frequency of the noise in texture space."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["UV Frequency"], "role": "item", "extent": [2415, 2433], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2497, 2532], "text": ["Offset the noise position."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["UV Offset"], "role": "item", "extent": [2482, 2497], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2556, 2589], "text": ["Displace amount of uv\u2019s."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["UV Noise Intensity"], "role": "item", "extent": [2532, 2556], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Noise"], "extent": [2088, 2104], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2629, 2668], "text": ["Create a vertex attribute, Cd."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Add Colour"], "role": "item", "extent": [2613, 2629], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2687, 2769], "text": ["Switch the ramp from using the u direction to the v direction of the uv\u2019s."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["V Colour Ramp"], "role": "item", "extent": [2668, 2687], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Vertex Colour"], "extent": [2589, 2613], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "extent": [593, 605], "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}], "summary": [" Create a polygon disc with uv\u2019s and normals "], "type": "root", "attrs": {"version": null, "tags": "sidefxlabs, model, sidefxlabs", "namespace": "labs", "internal": "labs::disc_generator", "context": "sop", "type": "node", "icon": "SOP/circle"}, "title": ["Labs Disc Generator"]}